queries.sql: SELECT MONTHNAME(tanggal) AS nama_bulan, YEAR(tanggal) AS tahun, SUM(kas_masuk) AS total_kas_masuk, SUM(kas_keluar) AS total_kas_keluar FROM tbl_kas_masjid WHERE tanggal >= DATE_SUB(CURDATE(), INTERVAL 6 MONTH) AND (kas_masuk IS NOT NULL OR kas_keluar IS NOT NULL) GROUP BY YEAR(tanggal), MONTH(tanggal) ORDER BY YEAR(tanggal) ASC, MONTH(tanggal) ASC
SELECT SUM(kas_masuk) AS total_kas_masuk FROM tbl_kas_masjid WHERE YEAR(tanggal) = YEAR(CURDATE()) AND MONTH(tanggal) = MONTH(CURDATE())
